{3000}{}{Oh man, from what hole are you coming from?}
{3010}{}{From that in the inside of the tent... [You point to the tent.]}
{4000}{}{You've been hiding from that sand storm yesterday? Some from our caravan followers got it pretty hard and we even lost one man back in the desert...}
{4010}{}{Who are you?}
{4020}{}{Can I ask you some questions? From survivor-to-survivor?}
{4030}{}{Yeah. Was nice to talk to you. Have to go now.}
{5000}{}{I'm J.D., everyone calls me like that and so do you.}
{5010}{}{Can I ask you some questions? From survivor-to-survivor?}
{5020}{}{Good, J.D., was nice to talk to you, but have to go now. Bye.}
{6000}{}{Sure. What do you want to know?}
{6010}{}{Can you tell me something about the surrounding area?}
{6020}{}{Where are you heading to?}
{6030}{}{Something interesting happened the last days or so?}
{6040}{}{Nevermind. Need to go.}
{7000}{}{The closest location from here is the Hub. It's the biggest trade center in the south. You should check it out. In the south you will find the Boneyard. Adytum is deep in the ruins and a dangerous place. In the north west you will meet the Brotherhood of Steel. But if I would be you, I wouldn't go there. Scary people.}
{7010}{}{Tell me about the Hub.}
{7020}{}{I want to ask you something else.}
{8000}{}{We are moving to the Hub. Should be there in a day or so. }
{8010}{}{I want to ask you something else.}
{8020}{}{Tell me about the Hub.}
