{9010}{}{I want to ask you something else.}
{10000}{}{Well, what to say. It's a big place with many traders. A lot caravans enter and exit every few hours. You should see it by yourself.}
{10010}{}{Can I travel with you guys?}
{10020}{}{That's all I wanted to know. See you.}
{11000}{}{Nah, we are full here. Also we will stay for a little while on this place and rest. But... you could do something for me.}
{11010}{}{And what?}
{11020}{}{Better not. I am running out of time already. Bye.}
