{12010}{}{Sure. Sounds simple.}
{12020}{}{I don't think I will be able to do that. I am moving into a completely different direction.}
{13000}{}{Well, then. Tell me when you changed your plans.}
{13010}{}{Yeah. But now I have a question again.}
{13020}{}{I will. See you.}
{14000}{}{Great! Tell our boss, we will be there in like one or two days.}
{14010}{}{I am on my way...}
